OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,FITV News US Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,7,Freports from Washington DC
OL,9,FPresident Donald Trump and other top
OL,10,FWhite House officials were evacuated
OL,11,Ffrom an annual dinner of the White
OL,12,FHouse Correspondents' Association
OL,13,Fafter a man armed with guns and knives
OL,14,Fstormed the lobby and opened fire.
OL,16,FThe president was unharmed.
OL,18,FThe shooting suspect was taken into
OL,19,Fcustody and identified as Cole Tomas
OL,20,FAllen, 31, from Torrance, California,
OL,21,Flaw enforcement officials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
