OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777246395
OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,FThe suspect worked as a teacher and a
OL,7,Fvideo game developer, according to
OL,8,Freports by ITV News' US partner CNN.
OL,10,FTrump described the man as "a lone
OL,11,Fwolf whack job" in a post on Truth
OL,12,FSocial, where he also posted a picture
OL,13,Fof the alleged assailant.
OL,15,FHe is understood to have been a guest
OL,16,Fin the Washington Hilton hotel where
OL,17,Fthe event was being held and faces
OL,18,Fcharges including assaulting an
OL,19,Fofficer with a dangerous weapon, but
OL,20,Facting attorney general Todd Blanche
OL,21,Fsaid additional charges will be filed.
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@OO]
