OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOne officer, who was shot but
OL,12,Fprotected by his bulletproof vest, was
OL,13,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,15,FA motive was not immediately known,
OL,16,Fand acting Attorney General Todd
OL,17,FBlanche said charges related to
OL,18,FSaturday night's attack will be filed
OL,19,Fshortly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
