OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777246395
OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,FThe president praised the secret
OL,7,Fservice and said the gunman was not
OL,8,Fclose to breaching the ballroom where
OL,9,Fhe sat on stage at the time of the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FWashington mayor Muriel Bowser said
OL,13,Fshe had "no reason" to believe anyone
OL,14,Felse was involved.
OL,16,FTrump added: "I saw a room that was
OL,17,Fjust totally unified. It was, in one
OL,18,Fway, very beautiful, a very beautiful
OL,19,Fthing.
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@SO]xD@NOU
