OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777246395
OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,F"To see a man charge a security
OL,7,Fcheckpoint armed with multiple
OL,8,Fweapons, and he was taken down by some
OL,9,Fvery brave members of secret service,
OL,10,Fand they acted very quickly."
OL,12,FTrump has vowed to reschedule the
OL,13,Fdisrupted event at a late-night press
OL,14,Fconference following the shooting.
OL,16,FHe was attending the annual dinner for
OL,17,Fthe first time as president.
