OL,3,CTrump evacuated following shooting at
OL,4,CWhite House journalists' dinner
OL,6,FIt was the third time since 2024 that
OL,7,Fthe president had been under threat by
OL,8,Fan attacker in his immediate vicinity,
OL,9,Fincluding the assassination attempt in
OL,10,FButler, Pennsylvania, that injured him
OL,11,Fand killed a local firefighter.
OL,13,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,14,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,15,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,16,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
